race.comment: SCOUNDREL (2) is a consistent conveyance hitting the top-five in 11 of 12 career starts and this is not an overly strong affair. Should be able to take a position up on speed and will give backers a sight. BONJOUR RUPERT (8) has been right there at the past few efforts and is sure to get a gun run in transit from gate three. Should be hitting the line with gusto. IONACELTIC (1) is having his first run for the new stable but looked good saluting at Dalby last time out and any push in betting must be respected. PRIDE OF SAVABELLA (10) strips fitter second-up from the spell and may earn some minor money. PERRI LASS (7) next in line with the 2kg claim.
